Title: To Halve and to Hold
Plot: When a single human bone is discovered in the desert, Grissom and Catherine must cover miles of territory to find the rest of the skeleton. Warrick and Sarah trace the death of a male stripper to members of a wedding party who may have celebrated a little too hard the night before the nuptials.
GuestStars: Eileen Ryan, Dorie Barton, Lisa Dean Ryan, Ele Keats, Christopher Jacobs, Palmer Davis, Bobby G, Colby G., Jan-Michael Vincent
